\"><\/a><strong>What is Usability Testing<\/strong><\/h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The path to digital transformation is restricted with multiple challenges. Together with delivering a flawless website or application, one of the key challenges that is faced is the changing nature of user expectations. A happy user cannot guarantee another. With the advancement of Omni-channel, users are looking for a comprehensive website\/application experience.<\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This has resulted in extreme pressure on enterprises to measure and improve user experience across various modes of usage. However, if a product is properly launched with thorough usability testing, it will help in attracting users and make them stick to your website or application, resulting in a rise in business growth.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a style=\"position: relative; top: -80px;\" name=\"Usability testing infographic | Experience UX\"><\/a><strong>Usability testing infographic | Experience UX<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In this infographic, we will discuss the importance of user experience and how usability testing can help you achieve that.<\/p>\r\n<img src=\"https:\/\/www.testingxperts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Usability-Testing02.png\" alt=\"usability-testing02\" \/>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Contents 1. What is Usability Testing 2. Usability testing infographic | Experience UX What is Usability Testing The path to digital transformation is restricted with multiple challenges. Together with delivering a flawless website or application, one of the key challenges that is faced is the changing nature of user expectations. A happy user cannot guarantee &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.testingxperts.com\/blog\/usability-testing-the-key-to-a-flawless-user-experience-infographic\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> &#8220;Usability Testing: Key to a Flawless User Experience&#8221;<\/